com.thinkaurelius.titan.core.log

Interface LogProcessorFramework

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    StandardLogProcessorFramework

    public interface LogProcessorFramework
    Framework for processing transaction logs. Using the LogProcessorBuilder returned by addLogProcessor(String) one can process the change events for a particular transaction log identified by name.
    Author:
    Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
